ref.said:
"You are over scrupulous surely. I dare say Mr. Bingley will be very glad to see you;
              and I will send a few lines by you to assure him of my hearty consent to his marrying whichever he chooses of the girls; though I must throw in a
              good word for my little Lizzy."

